item.title: CVE-2020-9672|2024-08-04T10:34:39.917Z -- adobe -- adobe%20coldfusion%202016
item.description: Adobe ColdFusion 2016 update 15 and earlier versions, and ColdFusion 2018 update 9 and earlier versions have a dll search-order hijacking vulnerability. Successful exploitation could lead to privilege escalation.
